WEBVTT

00:00:00.913 --> 00:00:02.290
Believe it or not,

00:00:02.290 --> 00:00:03.875
many of you are participating

00:00:03.875 --> 00:00:07.295
in one of the greatest
democratizations of storytelling

00:00:07.295 --> 00:00:08.504
the world has ever known.

00:00:09.380 --> 00:00:12.383
And you’re probably doing this
on a daily basis

00:00:12.383 --> 00:00:14.719
through the movies
and TV shows you’re watching.

00:00:15.678 --> 00:00:20.141
This is a grand democratization
that’s giving voice on a global scale

00:00:20.141 --> 00:00:22.935
to the bizarre, fantastical
stories of the unheard.

00:00:23.436 --> 00:00:24.771
It’s amazing,

00:00:24.771 --> 00:00:26.522
and I want to tell you all about it.

00:00:27.356 --> 00:00:31.944
But first, to fully appreciate
everything I'm about to say,